cs.IT, cs.COMM, cs.SI, cs.NI, cs.DS 

This paper deals with information theory and communication systems, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.IT and cs.COMM. It also involves signal processing and network information theory, which fall under cs.SI and cs.NI respectively. Additionally, the paper discusses the decoding process, which is related to distributed systems and algorithms, covered by cs.DS.
